Description:
   Vigil Strike is the Sentinel's foundational combat technique: a deliberate
   blow delivered from a watched position. The Sentinel sees the opening
   before they take it. This is not a reactive attack — it is a strike made
   from a posture of sustained observation, placed at the moment the
   practitioner has already identified.

   Damage is calculated from pseudo-level and Strength (war_attack helper,
   same as Warden melee skills). The Sentinel shares a physical combat
   foundation with the Warden tradition, though the doctrinal emphasis
   differs: where a Warden holds ground, a Sentinel watches it.

   Syntax: vigil strike <target>
   Requires POS_FIGHTING. Can be practiced to improve hit rate.
